## Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/smallbizsecurity/smallbizsecurity.org.git
cd smallbizsecurity.org

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build
```

